videos.description: Kristina Nelson finds Marina Mabrey for a 3-pointer at the end of the first quarter to extend Notre Dame's lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: 3-pointer extends Notre Dame's lead

videos.description: J'Kyra Brown goes coast to coast and makes the and-1 layup at the end of the first half to cut Notre Dame's lead to 44-36.
videos.headline: Virginia keeps it close with layup

videos.description: J'Kyra Brown finds Jocelyn Willoughby for the corner 3-pointer to tie the game at 44.
videos.headline: Virginia gets off to strong start in second half

videos.description: Brianna Turner and Jackie Young finish off the back-to-back alley-oop layups early in the second half to give Notre Dame the lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: Back-to-back alley-oop layups put Notre Dame on top

videos.description: Breyana Mason makes the buzzer beater at the end of the 3rd quarter.
videos.headline: Virginia stays within striking distance with the jumper as time expires in 3rd Quarter

videos.description: Kathryn Westbeld makes the layup as time expires on the shot clock, Notre Dame beats Virginia 82-74.
videos.headline: Notre Dame scores at end of shot clock, hangs on to beat Virginia

videos.description: Roy Philpott and Brooke Weisbrod break down Notre Dame's victory over Virginia.
videos.headline: Long ball aids Notre Dame against Virginia

videos.description: Notre Dame coach Muffet McGraw evaluates her team's victory over Virginia.
videos.headline: McGraw: 'We have a long way to go'
